trend_summary: Built-up space gradually spreads from the central township toward east and south, filling former forest gaps and edging into farmland. Agricultural parcels remain dominant, yet more are fragmented. Road network thickens and a few industrial rooftops appear, but wide green blocks persist, keeping an overall semi-rural character.
